   
<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
 

  <Paragraph>
The Clock control supports both analog and digital mode for displaying time. Different visual skins, including Office 2007's Blue, Black, Silver and Blend theme can be applied. The appearance of the clock can also be completely customized using the various appearance properties available.
  </Paragraph>

  <Paragraph TextAlignment ="Center"><Image Source="Images\ClockDemo.png" Stretch="None" /></Paragraph> 
<BlockUIContainer>
  <TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">
	Features
  </TextBlock>
  </BlockUIContainer>

    <List>
    <ListItem><Paragraph>Hand dragging support</Paragraph></ListItem>
    <ListItem><Paragraph>Extensive designer support in both Expression Blend and Visual Studio 2008</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Properties to completely customize the control without the necessity of custom templates</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>A digital watch can be displayed to cross-check the time selected</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Built-in visual styles and themes support </Paragraph></ListItem>
  </List> 
<BlockUIContainer>
 <TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">
Interactive Features
</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>The flow direction of the Clock control can be changed by selecting the "Left-to-Right" or "Right-to-Left" radio button in the layout properties.</Paragraph></ListItem>

<ListItem><Paragraph>The various brushes and background options in the Clock Demo Custom Properties allows to change the look and feel of the Clock control.</Paragraph></ListItem>

<ListItem><Paragraph> The "AMPMSelectorCornerRadius" text box lets users change the AM-PM selector's corner radius in the Clock control.</Paragraph></ListItem>

<ListItem><Paragraph> The "FrameCornerRadius" text box allows users to change the frame's corner radius of the Clock control.</Paragraph></ListItem>

<ListItem><Paragraph> The "ClockCornerRadius" text box allows users to change the clock's corner radius.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>


 </FlowDocument>

